WEBVTT

00:01:47.820 --> 00:01:52.420
=Light of Dawn=

00:02:03.879 --> 00:02:04.439
Do not move.

00:02:06.200 --> 00:02:07.840
I know I cannot get away anymore.

00:02:08.680 --> 00:02:09.840
But still,

00:02:10.800 --> 00:02:13.520
there are things I want to
say to you and the girl.

00:02:14.120 --> 00:02:15.719
Do you really not want to know

00:02:15.719 --> 00:02:18.680
how your biological father,
Yang Wenyuan,

00:02:19.520 --> 00:02:20.840
actually died?

00:02:22.400 --> 00:02:24.639
Chen Kang will tell you
the time and place.

00:02:25.280 --> 00:02:26.759
Only you and Feifei come.

00:02:50.439 --> 00:02:52.360
Can you move her to another room?

00:02:58.280 --> 00:02:58.800
Mom.

00:03:01.130 --> 00:03:02.510
I've already talked to the doctor.

00:03:03.120 --> 00:03:05.199
You need a light,
high protein diet for now.

00:03:06.599 --> 00:03:07.879
I made crucian carp soup at home.

00:03:09.080 --> 00:03:11.800
I picked out all the bones for you.

00:03:15.759 --> 00:03:16.360
Gao Feng.

00:03:18.439 --> 00:03:20.879
I owe you an apology
on Gao Dahua's behalf.

00:03:30.280 --> 00:03:30.800
Mom.

00:03:31.039 --> 00:03:31.960
Don't call me Mom.

00:03:33.680 --> 00:03:34.439
I don't deserve it.

00:03:36.360 --> 00:03:37.879
After what Gao Dahua did,

00:03:38.800 --> 00:03:40.800
I no longer deserve
to hear you call me that.

00:03:42.280 --> 00:03:43.199
What's going on?

00:03:46.159 --> 00:03:47.919
So much has happened lately.

00:03:49.960 --> 00:03:51.680
I've already found my biological mother,

00:03:52.800 --> 00:03:54.840
and the truth
about my background is almost clear.

00:03:55.680 --> 00:03:56.360
And yet,

00:03:58.960 --> 00:04:00.039
you don't want me anymore.

00:04:07.400 --> 00:04:08.960
How could I not want you?

00:04:11.100 --> 00:04:12.990
Gao Feng,
these past couple of days lying here,

00:04:13.960 --> 00:04:16.319
everything in my head
keeps replaying like a movie.

00:04:17.720 --> 00:04:19.100
I kept thinking and thinking,

00:04:19.110 --> 00:04:21.319
and there are so many things
I just can't figure out.

00:04:22.160 --> 00:04:24.199
All my life, following Gao Dahua,

00:04:24.680 --> 00:04:27.000
we never lived
a rich or privileged life.

00:04:27.160 --> 00:04:28.600
I never asked for wealth.

00:04:28.920 --> 00:04:30.839
All I wanted was to live honestly,

00:04:30.839 --> 00:04:32.480
and to have a child.

00:04:34.480 --> 00:04:36.639
When Gao Dahua brought you home,

00:04:37.519 --> 00:04:39.639
I knew I had a son. I...

00:04:40.600 --> 00:04:42.439
From that moment on,

00:04:42.439 --> 00:04:44.519
I knew I would owe him
for the rest of my life.

00:04:46.600 --> 00:04:49.000
He carried such a huge secret
in his heart.

00:04:49.040 --> 00:04:50.000
He couldn't tell me,

00:04:50.000 --> 00:04:51.399
and he couldn't tell you either.

00:04:54.480 --> 00:04:56.319
So he drove himself to ruin.

00:04:57.730 --> 00:04:59.959
In the end, you could say
he paid for it with his life.

00:05:03.639 --> 00:05:04.800
How is your recovery?

00:05:06.120 --> 00:05:06.879
Pretty good.

00:05:08.170 --> 00:05:09.920
After I found out Gao Feng
was your brother,

00:05:11.120 --> 00:05:12.279
I was actually really happy.

00:05:14.300 --> 00:05:16.040
Don't you think
relationships between people

00:05:16.040 --> 00:05:17.250
can be something truly amazing?

00:05:19.279 --> 00:05:22.160
Sometimes you meet someone
for the first time

00:05:23.550 --> 00:05:24.879
and it already feels like family.

00:05:28.600 --> 00:05:31.399
You're also the person closest
to Gao Feng now.

00:05:33.040 --> 00:05:34.040
I want to know,

00:05:35.079 --> 00:05:37.079
what kind of person is he in your eyes?

00:05:44.279 --> 00:05:45.680
I'd like to know that too.

00:05:47.600 --> 00:05:50.000
We failed you, Gao Feng.

00:05:51.519 --> 00:05:53.240
We truly failed you.

00:05:53.240 --> 00:05:53.759
Mom.

00:05:55.160 --> 00:05:56.360
Please listen to me carefully.

00:05:57.360 --> 00:05:58.920
You spent half your life living for him,

00:05:58.920 --> 00:06:00.210
and half your life living for me.

00:06:01.600 --> 00:06:03.279
Can't you live for yourself now?

00:06:04.839 --> 00:06:06.790
From now on,
all of us should live for ourselves.

00:06:11.360 --> 00:06:12.519
All these past years,

00:06:14.279 --> 00:06:15.639
whether love or hatred,

00:06:18.079 --> 00:06:20.150
the people who've died,
and everything from the past,

00:06:21.240 --> 00:06:22.600
have trapped me for far too long.

00:06:23.720 --> 00:06:24.800
But I know very clearly

00:06:26.560 --> 00:06:27.680
that it's all over now.

00:06:28.800 --> 00:06:30.600
I used to be obsessed
with finding the truth,

00:06:31.879 --> 00:06:33.519
with no room to live my own life.

00:06:35.240 --> 00:06:36.639
But people grow up.

00:06:38.959 --> 00:06:40.120
Now I finally see it clearly.

00:06:41.160 --> 00:06:42.079
What you gave me

00:06:43.519 --> 00:06:44.240
was real.

00:06:50.319 --> 00:06:51.199
So now,

00:06:53.279 --> 00:06:54.720
we should all move forward.

00:06:55.839 --> 00:06:56.360
Yes.

00:07:02.240 --> 00:07:03.759
You will always be my son,

00:07:05.839 --> 00:07:07.319
my very best son.

00:07:47.160 --> 00:07:47.839
What's wrong?

00:07:50.319 --> 00:07:51.439
Wu Guohao sent word.

00:07:52.120 --> 00:07:53.120
He wants to see me.

00:07:54.639 --> 00:07:56.000
The police are about to catch him.

00:07:57.040 --> 00:07:59.190
When someone is cornered,
they're capable of anything.

00:07:59.759 --> 00:08:01.160
For him to reach out to you now,

00:08:02.519 --> 00:08:03.360
aren't you afraid?

00:08:04.480 --> 00:08:05.600
I was scared before.

00:08:06.600 --> 00:08:09.279
But now that it's come to this,
I'm not anymore.

00:08:10.279 --> 00:08:11.199
But I am.

00:08:14.959 --> 00:08:17.639
All this time,
you were digging into your past,

00:08:18.120 --> 00:08:20.160
turning all of Binchuan upside down.

00:08:20.720 --> 00:08:22.279
You were walking on the edge every day,

00:08:22.480 --> 00:08:23.839
and I supported you the whole way.

00:08:24.480 --> 00:08:25.600
But this time is different.

00:08:33.519 --> 00:08:34.519
I'll come back.

00:08:35.799 --> 00:08:36.960
Can you trust me just once?

00:08:38.600 --> 00:08:39.879
I've been an orphan for so long.

00:08:40.500 --> 00:08:41.600
It's time to change my fate.

00:09:19.300 --> 00:09:23.020
=Episode 18=
=Repay=

