♪I give long roads
to the distant horizon♪

00:09:49.780 --> 00:09:53.420
♪I give roses to love♪

00:09:53.780 --> 00:09:56.500
♪What can I give you♪

00:09:56.500 --> 00:10:00.060
♪My lover?♪

00:10:01.860 --> 00:10:05.260
♪I give white clouds to the meadow♪

00:10:05.620 --> 00:10:09.300
♪I give rivers to the ocean♪

00:10:09.700 --> 00:10:12.220
♪What can I give you♪

00:10:12.220 --> 00:10:16.020
♪My friend?♪

00:10:26.710 --> 00:10:28.000
I already talked to the police.

00:10:29.519 --> 00:10:30.919
I was just worried about you.

00:10:31.000 --> 00:10:33.490
I thought you might not be used to
staying in a hotel like this,

00:10:34.039 --> 00:10:35.560
so I bought you some daily essentials.

00:10:36.279 --> 00:10:37.720
Some common medicine,

00:10:38.300 --> 00:10:39.200
and health supplements.

00:10:40.039 --> 00:10:41.399
A face mask and an eye mask.

00:10:41.810 --> 00:10:43.759
Most importantly,
these sheets and duvet covers.

00:10:44.480 --> 00:10:45.720
I'll change them for you first.

00:10:46.279 --> 00:10:47.159
Just make do for now.

00:11:06.840 --> 00:11:08.279
It's still early for that.

00:11:11.360 --> 00:11:11.919
I know.

00:11:12.960 --> 00:11:15.720
I just happened to pass
a maternity and baby store,

00:11:16.279 --> 00:11:18.519
and saw all those tiny clothes
and little socks.

00:11:20.200 --> 00:11:21.399
They were just too cute.

00:11:24.300 --> 00:11:25.820
I couldn't help myself and bought them.

00:11:27.879 --> 00:11:29.240
Isn't fate strange?

00:11:30.279 --> 00:11:33.240
I always thought I was just an orphan.

00:11:35.360 --> 00:11:36.399
And suddenly,

00:11:38.320 --> 00:11:39.320
I'm going to be an uncle.

00:11:40.800 --> 00:11:42.430
I'm not very good
at buying these things.

00:11:42.440 --> 00:11:43.600
They might be a bit big.

00:11:44.559 --> 00:11:45.440
But that's okay.

00:11:45.799 --> 00:11:48.080
In a few years, when the child grows up,

00:11:49.100 --> 00:11:49.990
they'll fit just fine.

00:11:51.039 --> 00:11:51.799
Thank you.

00:12:14.039 --> 00:12:14.720
Well,

00:12:15.279 --> 00:12:18.000
there are some steam eye masks in there.

00:12:19.080 --> 00:12:20.039
They help you sleep.

00:12:21.360 --> 00:12:21.879
You…

00:12:24.570 --> 00:12:25.360
Get some good rest.

00:12:42.400 --> 00:12:44.080
The reason we even met
in the first place

00:12:44.080 --> 00:12:46.090
was because neither of us knew
who we really were.

00:12:46.519 --> 00:12:48.519
We worked together to get to the truth.

00:12:49.399 --> 00:12:50.130
Just the two of us.

00:12:53.600 --> 00:12:54.879
But whatever bond we had,

00:12:56.190 --> 00:12:57.120
this is where it ends.

00:12:58.720 --> 00:12:59.960
Wu Feifei, don't do this.

00:13:16.010 --> 00:13:17.200
What's this supposed to mean?

00:13:18.120 --> 00:13:19.080
Nothing special.

00:13:20.000 --> 00:13:22.440
I just thought it was worth keeping.

00:13:22.879 --> 00:13:24.480
Two people who are actually siblings,

00:13:24.480 --> 00:13:26.279
calling each other besties for a while.

00:13:28.960 --> 00:13:29.919
Isn't that interesting?

00:13:30.320 --> 00:13:31.360
I'll leave it with you.

00:13:39.639 --> 00:13:40.840
We promised each other

00:13:41.320 --> 00:13:42.759
no lies between us, right?

00:13:46.879 --> 00:13:47.720
He asked to meet me.

00:13:48.480 --> 00:13:49.399
He asked you alone?

00:13:49.639 --> 00:13:51.190
Both of us, but I want to go by myself.

00:13:51.240 --> 00:13:51.879
Why?

00:13:52.279 --> 00:13:53.440
This isn't just about you.

00:13:53.679 --> 00:13:55.000
And you should tell the police.

00:13:55.000 --> 00:13:56.279
He still has people helping him.

00:13:56.280 --> 00:13:57.990
That makes it even
more dangerous to go alone.

00:13:58.260 --> 00:14:00.080
I can't even be sure
what he's capable of now.

00:14:00.080 --> 00:14:01.200
We're so close.

00:14:02.399 --> 00:14:03.039
Yang Wenyuan,

00:14:04.399 --> 00:14:05.360
our father,

00:14:06.000 --> 00:14:07.039
I have to know the truth.

00:14:10.639 --> 00:14:11.600
I'm going with you.

00:14:14.000 --> 00:14:15.279
Right now, in this world,

00:14:15.279 --> 00:14:16.399
you're my only family.

00:14:18.279 --> 00:14:19.879
Those little shoes and tiny clothes,

00:14:21.200 --> 00:14:23.159
you can put them
on your nephew yourself someday.

00:14:25.840 --> 00:14:27.279
Both of us have to survive this.

00:14:36.600 --> 00:14:37.080
Feng.

00:14:41.639 --> 00:14:42.559
Don't leave me behind.

00:14:42.559 --> 00:14:43.820
♪For an answer♪

00:14:43.820 --> 00:14:46.460
♪You stand guard alone outside the door♪

00:14:48.020 --> 00:14:50.660
♪The obsession held within is sharp♪

00:14:50.660 --> 00:14:53.519
♪It cuts through everything,
leaving no way back♪

00:14:53.519 --> 00:14:54.240
Su Min.

00:14:55.440 --> 00:14:56.559
Wu Guohao asked to meet me.

00:14:57.000 --> 00:14:58.320
Please approve my plan.

00:15:02.060 --> 00:15:07.300
♪Fate hangs above your head
like a suspended blade♪

