♪Why is the truth
always buried in thorns♪

00:15:35.100 --> 00:15:36.860
♪The light will come♪

00:15:38.799 --> 00:15:40.600
Wu Guohao is extremely arrogant.

00:15:41.120 --> 00:15:42.390
The evidence is already airtight,

00:15:42.879 --> 00:15:44.879
yet he still thinks he can walk free.

00:15:45.720 --> 00:15:48.799
The International Club he controlled,
along with its series of crimes,

00:15:49.039 --> 00:15:51.240
may be an extreme case from the 1990s,

00:15:51.480 --> 00:15:52.480
but the nature is vile,

00:15:52.720 --> 00:15:53.559
and the harm immense.

00:15:54.519 --> 00:15:55.039
Su Min.

00:15:55.160 --> 00:15:57.200
Mobilize citywide police forces
and lock this down.

00:15:57.840 --> 00:15:59.200
Wu Guohao

00:15:59.639 --> 00:16:00.919
and his entire criminal network

00:16:01.279 --> 00:16:02.639
must face justice.

00:16:02.960 --> 00:16:03.919
- Yes.
- Yes.

00:17:06.000 --> 00:17:06.839
Everyone's here.

00:17:07.920 --> 00:17:09.680
Come on. Let's have a drink.

00:17:15.599 --> 00:17:16.279
Feifei.

00:17:17.640 --> 00:17:18.680
How have you been lately?

00:17:19.960 --> 00:17:23.079
Now that you've found your real brother,
you've forgotten your dad?

00:17:24.440 --> 00:17:25.119
Call me Dad.

00:17:29.039 --> 00:17:29.680
Call me Dad!

00:17:31.880 --> 00:17:32.640
What are you doing?

00:17:34.680 --> 00:17:36.000
You came prepared, didn't you?

00:17:37.640 --> 00:17:39.160
Anyone who wanted me dead

00:17:40.680 --> 00:17:42.079
is already buried underground.

00:17:45.680 --> 00:17:48.240
The girl I raised for over twenty years,

00:17:52.160 --> 00:17:54.039
I just want to see her once.

00:17:58.319 --> 00:18:00.079
And I have to go through you to do it?

00:18:02.559 --> 00:18:05.319
Tell them how you died.

00:18:13.680 --> 00:18:14.400
I forgot.

00:18:15.720 --> 00:18:17.000
He can't speak.

00:18:17.519 --> 00:18:19.799
I smashed his jaw.

00:18:20.720 --> 00:18:21.240
Feifei.

00:18:22.200 --> 00:18:23.720
Do you remember when you were little,

00:18:23.720 --> 00:18:25.690
you were especially scared
of the scar on my hand?

00:18:26.680 --> 00:18:28.359
Whenever I held you,
you would pull away.

00:18:30.480 --> 00:18:32.079
Later on, I even went abroad

00:18:32.079 --> 00:18:33.720
and had several reconstructive surgeries

00:18:34.160 --> 00:18:35.279
before it was finally fixed.

00:18:35.839 --> 00:18:36.400
You forgot?

00:18:46.359 --> 00:18:47.039
Xu.

00:18:48.480 --> 00:18:51.880
Why are you still
such a pathetic coward?

00:18:52.160 --> 00:18:55.079
After all this time,
you still haven't moved on?

00:18:55.839 --> 00:18:58.200
You're still thinking about those lives,

00:18:58.200 --> 00:18:58.799
aren't you?

00:18:59.480 --> 00:19:00.680
Your heart condition

00:19:00.680 --> 00:19:03.559
came from your own indecision.

00:19:04.200 --> 00:19:04.880
Take a look.

00:19:05.480 --> 00:19:08.599
Look how grand Penglai Plaza is now.

00:19:10.359 --> 00:19:14.559
How many people
walk across it every day,

00:19:14.559 --> 00:19:15.759
coming and going.

00:19:16.400 --> 00:19:18.359
All that glory.

00:19:18.480 --> 00:19:20.839
What's a few buried bodies underneath?

00:19:21.839 --> 00:19:24.720
I always believed
there was friendship between us.

00:19:25.359 --> 00:19:27.200
I never wanted to grow old

00:19:27.200 --> 00:19:28.880
and end up this lonely.

00:19:29.400 --> 00:19:31.519
I built such a huge empire,

00:19:31.799 --> 00:19:34.079
yet in the end I can only sit alone,

00:19:35.480 --> 00:19:36.559
drinking old liquor,

00:19:37.240 --> 00:19:38.200
reliving the past.

00:19:39.160 --> 00:19:40.599
I gave you a chance.

00:19:41.480 --> 00:19:43.119
You betrayed me.

00:19:47.680 --> 00:19:48.599
You're here too.

00:19:51.400 --> 00:19:53.720
You think you're worthy
of sitting at this table?

00:19:54.200 --> 00:19:57.640
You're the one
who hid right under my nose,

00:19:58.079 --> 00:19:59.759
pulling the wool over everyone's eyes.

00:20:00.720 --> 00:20:01.839
Infertile, right?

00:20:02.400 --> 00:20:03.519
Desperate for a son, right?

00:20:04.000 --> 00:20:04.720
Well, here he is.

00:20:06.720 --> 00:20:08.599
The son you raised

00:20:08.799 --> 00:20:10.000
for over twenty years.

00:20:11.440 --> 00:20:12.839
Isn't that wonderful?

00:20:15.240 --> 00:20:16.039
So wonderful.

00:20:18.680 --> 00:20:20.359
Qu Meng,

00:20:22.079 --> 00:20:24.039
you really were unbelievably foolish.

00:20:25.079 --> 00:20:27.359
I had so many men under me,
yet after all that choosing,

00:20:27.359 --> 00:20:28.680
you picked a so called good man.

00:20:28.799 --> 00:20:29.960
That very good man,

00:20:30.200 --> 00:20:32.960
ended up burying you with his own hands.

00:20:34.640 --> 00:20:36.240
You were truly foolish.

00:20:42.319 --> 00:20:42.960
Hongyue.

00:20:45.440 --> 00:20:47.519
You really were blind.

00:20:48.079 --> 00:20:49.839
I have nothing left to say to you.

00:20:50.880 --> 00:20:51.480
Enough.

00:20:52.440 --> 00:20:55.599
Today, we board the old boat
to meet old friends.

00:20:56.599 --> 00:20:57.920
But after today,

00:20:58.519 --> 00:21:00.400
I will leave Binchuan.

00:21:01.880 --> 00:21:04.519
And you should
go beneath Binchuan as well,

00:21:05.960 --> 00:21:07.400
to rest in peace.

00:21:07.400 --> 00:21:08.980
You really think you can still get away?

00:21:13.240 --> 00:21:14.319
Of course I can.

00:21:15.039 --> 00:21:16.359
And I'll leave

00:21:17.160 --> 00:21:19.319
clearly and in full glory.

00:21:19.920 --> 00:21:20.920
I even made a point

00:21:22.039 --> 00:21:24.599
of preparing a special gift
for the two of you.

00:21:35.039 --> 00:21:38.079
Let today count as your birthday.

00:21:39.200 --> 00:21:41.079
This birthday is from me.

00:21:42.960 --> 00:21:45.680
Yang Wenyuan and Qu Meng
never gave you one.

00:21:56.559 --> 00:21:59.720
♪Happy birthday to you♪

00:22:00.279 --> 00:22:03.160
♪Happy birthday to you both♪

00:22:03.839 --> 00:22:06.799
♪Happy birthday to you♪

00:22:06.799 --> 00:22:07.990
Have you lost your mind enough?

00:22:12.440 --> 00:22:14.440
How can you talk
to your father like that?

00:22:14.880 --> 00:22:16.160
We were father and daughter once.

00:22:18.839 --> 00:22:20.319
That bond was rare enough.

