You used to be the person
I admired most.

00:22:25.880 --> 00:22:27.359
Don't let all those past years

00:22:30.000 --> 00:22:31.680
turn into a joke in the end.

00:22:34.000 --> 00:22:36.440
Wu Guohao,
no matter what you're still plotting,

00:22:36.880 --> 00:22:39.119
whether you plan to take
us hostage to escape,

00:22:39.119 --> 00:22:40.480
or drag us down with you,

00:22:41.599 --> 00:22:42.200
it won't work.

00:22:43.000 --> 00:22:45.240
Today's Binchuan is no longer something
you can control.

00:22:48.039 --> 00:22:48.920
Turn yourself in.

00:22:51.319 --> 00:22:54.160
So the two of you see me as a clown now?

00:22:57.680 --> 00:22:59.559
Some things, if I don't say them,

00:23:00.279 --> 00:23:03.240
you may never know
for the rest of your lives.

00:23:07.400 --> 00:23:09.920
I never left Binchuan
these past few days.

00:23:10.039 --> 00:23:11.720
I stayed here waiting for this,

00:23:11.720 --> 00:23:13.559
the DNA test report.

00:23:14.480 --> 00:23:15.599
I haven't opened it.

00:23:15.759 --> 00:23:16.880
I was waiting for you.

00:23:17.839 --> 00:23:19.039
Let's look at it together.

00:23:23.519 --> 00:23:24.079
Captain Su.

00:23:24.799 --> 00:23:26.640
The DNA test results
for Gao Feng and Wu Feifei

00:23:26.640 --> 00:23:28.359
in relation to Yang Wenyuan are out.

00:23:40.759 --> 00:23:41.839
Then I'll open it.

00:24:06.160 --> 00:24:07.119
We

00:24:08.119 --> 00:24:09.880
are not biologically related.

00:24:09.880 --> 00:24:11.300
(Confirmed: No biological relationship)

00:24:12.580 --> 00:24:13.740
Take a look.

00:24:15.279 --> 00:24:17.599
That's fine.

00:24:19.319 --> 00:24:20.400
That's fine.

00:24:22.400 --> 00:24:23.680
You can leave now.

00:24:24.200 --> 00:24:24.799
Get out.

00:24:28.119 --> 00:24:29.240
Get out now!

00:24:42.480 --> 00:24:45.240
You want revenge
for your mother, don't you?

00:24:47.839 --> 00:24:48.480
Come on.

00:24:57.039 --> 00:24:57.759
Come.

00:24:58.359 --> 00:24:59.000
Wu Guohao.

00:25:00.759 --> 00:25:01.599
You're calculating,

00:25:03.039 --> 00:25:03.799
and so am I.

00:25:04.440 --> 00:25:05.720
Lately I've been thinking,

00:25:06.240 --> 00:25:07.920
why it is that the two of us

00:25:08.440 --> 00:25:10.039
so often arrive at the same conclusions.

00:25:11.559 --> 00:25:12.240
The attic.

00:25:12.480 --> 00:25:13.160
Hongyue.

00:25:13.759 --> 00:25:14.559
Xu Zhiyang.

00:25:16.000 --> 00:25:17.790
That's right.
I'm always one step behind you.

00:25:18.400 --> 00:25:19.650
But afterward, when I look back,

00:25:20.200 --> 00:25:21.720
I realize I always understand you.

00:25:24.359 --> 00:25:25.480
The Penglai office

00:25:25.480 --> 00:25:26.799
was cleaned spotless.

00:25:26.799 --> 00:25:28.750
But after living in Binchuan
for so many years,

00:25:30.319 --> 00:25:33.160
it's not that hard to find traces
you left behind.

00:25:34.440 --> 00:25:35.960
This is an expedited DNA test report

00:25:35.960 --> 00:25:37.720
I had the city bureau run.

00:25:38.400 --> 00:25:39.480
Want to take a look?

00:26:05.500 --> 00:26:07.000
You swallowed a blank sheet of paper.

00:26:08.100 --> 00:26:09.790
If you don't believe me,
see for yourself.

00:26:13.880 --> 00:26:15.400
I never did

00:26:15.400 --> 00:26:16.599
any DNA test at all.

00:26:19.039 --> 00:26:20.079
So I won the bet.

00:26:22.079 --> 00:26:23.119
The report you had

00:26:24.519 --> 00:26:25.519
was fake too.

00:26:29.359 --> 00:26:30.079
This time,

00:26:30.480 --> 00:26:31.720
I was one step ahead of you.

00:26:39.000 --> 00:26:41.559
You know perfectly well
what the truth is.

00:26:42.680 --> 00:26:43.690
As for who you really are,

00:26:45.160 --> 00:26:46.480
I honestly don't care at all,

00:26:48.000 --> 00:26:49.990
because you don't even
deserve to be called human.

00:26:58.100 --> 00:27:02.260
(Early 1990s)

00:28:24.640 --> 00:28:26.079
You monster.

00:28:26.480 --> 00:28:28.039
I'll be waiting for you in hell.

00:28:58.960 --> 00:29:00.079
My teeth.

00:29:00.720 --> 00:29:02.359
You knocked my teeth out.

00:29:04.279 --> 00:29:05.079
Open your mouth.

00:29:14.640 --> 00:29:16.440
How did you figure it out?

00:29:17.359 --> 00:29:18.240
Someone like you

00:29:18.450 --> 00:29:19.559
would never fail to confirm

00:29:19.559 --> 00:29:21.360
your blood relationship
with your daughter.

00:29:21.440 --> 00:29:23.000
You must have tested Feifei long ago,

00:29:23.700 --> 00:29:25.790
otherwise you would never
have kept her by your side.

00:29:27.839 --> 00:29:30.160
Why dig it up to the very end

00:29:31.440 --> 00:29:32.839
like Qu Meng did?

00:29:33.000 --> 00:29:34.990
Because digging to the end
is the only way to reach the truth.

00:29:38.720 --> 00:29:39.880
The very fact that we exist

00:29:40.880 --> 00:29:42.680
is proof of all the evil you committed.

00:29:43.400 --> 00:29:45.359
You think that by pretending
to cut ties with us,

00:29:46.360 --> 00:29:48.200
you could erase
every trace you left behind,

00:29:48.599 --> 00:29:49.640
and escape your crimes?

00:29:52.960 --> 00:29:56.720
Wu Guohao, you spent your whole life
deceiving yourself,

00:29:56.720 --> 00:29:58.519
but we are not like you.

00:30:03.119 --> 00:30:04.480
I've already found our mother.

00:30:06.640 --> 00:30:09.079
I now know how brave she was
to give birth to us,

00:30:11.240 --> 00:30:13.000
and how cruel the evil inflicted

00:30:13.640 --> 00:30:14.680
upon her truly was.

00:30:17.200 --> 00:30:19.440
You could never
be that blank sheet of paper.

00:30:21.000 --> 00:30:22.119
All my searching

00:30:22.119 --> 00:30:23.300
has finally made me understand

00:30:23.559 --> 00:30:24.960
that love and choice

00:30:25.519 --> 00:30:26.799
matter more than anything else.

00:30:29.759 --> 00:30:31.039
And it also taught us

00:30:31.799 --> 00:30:33.559
what truly deserves to be protected.

00:30:34.640 --> 00:30:35.599
Standing before me,

00:30:35.599 --> 00:30:37.039
you are an enemy and a criminal,

00:30:37.520 --> 00:30:39.039
and you will inevitably face justice.

00:30:39.599 --> 00:30:40.519
Aside from your crimes,

00:30:42.480 --> 00:30:44.920
you will leave nothing behind.

00:31:14.119 --> 00:31:14.920
Wu.

00:31:17.279 --> 00:31:18.319
Wu.

00:31:19.960 --> 00:31:21.160
Turn yourself in.

00:31:56.200 --> 00:31:57.079
Sniper in position.

00:32:01.000 --> 00:32:01.839
Contact headquarters.

00:32:01.839 --> 00:32:03.180
Transmit the live feed to command.

00:32:37.200 --> 00:32:38.680
Report. There is a bomb on the ship.

00:32:39.620 --> 00:32:40.790
Evacuate everyone immediately.

00:32:51.800 --> 00:32:52.690
Don't come any closer.

00:32:55.759 --> 00:32:57.559
Don't move.

00:32:58.319 --> 00:32:59.359
You still have a chance.

00:33:03.200 --> 00:33:04.880
I don't have one anymore.

00:33:16.279 --> 00:33:18.200
If the hostages are in danger,

00:33:18.620 --> 00:33:19.720
you are authorized to shoot.

00:33:21.519 --> 00:33:21.960
Understood.

00:33:23.279 --> 00:33:24.240
You won't fire.

00:33:25.519 --> 00:33:26.400
I will.

00:33:28.039 --> 00:33:28.920
You won't.

00:33:30.880 --> 00:33:32.000
You never will.

00:34:18.480 --> 00:34:19.480
Dad!

00:34:37.920 --> 00:34:38.440
Master.

00:34:38.500 --> 00:34:39.599
Chen Kang has been subdued.

00:34:39.880 --> 00:34:41.599
All bombs on the ship
have been dismantled.

00:34:42.119 --> 00:34:43.079
Wu Guohao

00:34:43.079 --> 00:34:44.519
kept resisting to the very end.

00:35:27.320 --> 00:35:28.599
I never imagined Wu Guohao

00:35:30.159 --> 00:35:32.039
would leave in this way.

00:35:34.079 --> 00:35:36.119
He didn't dare
face the judgment of the law,

00:35:37.199 --> 00:35:39.199
and even less the judgment
of his own blood.

00:35:41.800 --> 00:35:43.159
Cause and effect of good and evil

00:35:44.159 --> 00:35:45.360
cannot be stopped by anyone.

00:35:47.800 --> 00:35:49.280
Just like this rushing river,

00:35:49.280 --> 00:35:50.880
it will always flow into the sea.

00:35:51.440 --> 00:35:53.079
No one can make it run backward.

00:35:54.119 --> 00:35:54.880
Wu Guohao

00:35:56.480 --> 00:35:57.480
got what he deserved.

00:36:06.140 --> 00:36:08.741
(After investigation, the People's Court publicly tried Wu Guohao,
the Penglai Group, and related individuals.)

00:36:08.742 --> 00:36:11.482
(Wu Guohao was charged with intentional homicide, arson, rape,
drug trafficking, and organizing prostitution.)

00:36:11.483 --> 00:36:13.766
(He was also charged with organizing and leading a criminal syndicate, unlawful detention, harboring criminals, and other offenses.)

00:36:13.767 --> 00:36:16.146
(Wu Feifei was convicted of intentional injury, perjury,
and harboring criminals, and sentenced to seven years in prison.)

00:36:16.147 --> 00:36:18.342
(Due to pregnancy, and in accordance with Chinese law,
her sentence was temporarily served outside prison.)

00:36:18.343 --> 00:36:20.178
(Xu Zhiyang was convicted of perjury and harboring criminals,
and sentenced to four years in prison.)

00:36:20.179 --> 00:36:22.380
(Due to serious illness and inability to care for himself,
his sentence was also temporarily served outside prison.)

00:36:22.380 --> 00:36:24.508
(Zhao Tianming was convicted of intentional homicide,
organizing prostitution, and drug trafficking.)

00:36:24.509 --> 00:36:26.535
(Combined with arson, harboring criminals,
and perjury, he was sentenced to death.)

00:36:26.536 --> 00:36:28.755
(Chen Kang was convicted of arson, intentional injury,
kidnapping, unlawful detention, and harboring criminals.)

00:36:28.756 --> 00:36:31.581
(For multiple crimes combined, he was sentenced to fifteen years in prison.)

00:36:31.582 --> 00:36:33.418
(The Mingyue Care Center was confirmed
to be an unlawful detention site and has been shut down.)

00:36:33.419 --> 00:36:34.846
(All women who were unlawfully detained have been rescued.)

00:36:34.847 --> 00:36:37.220
(All illegal proceeds of the Penglai Group have been recovered,
confiscated, compensated, and returned.)

00:37:03.079 --> 00:37:03.840
Dawg.

00:37:07.800 --> 00:37:08.840
Dawg, you're awake.

00:37:10.559 --> 00:37:11.159
Dawg.

00:37:13.159 --> 00:37:14.400
I'll go get the doctor.

00:37:19.199 --> 00:37:20.079
Don't go.

00:37:24.760 --> 00:37:25.480
I won't.

00:37:27.639 --> 00:37:28.199
I won't go.

00:37:30.039 --> 00:37:30.599
Okay.

00:37:32.000 --> 00:37:33.679
It feels like I just had

00:37:35.719 --> 00:37:36.440
a long dream.

00:37:39.280 --> 00:37:40.039
Don't be afraid.

00:37:41.800 --> 00:37:42.920
The dream is over.

00:37:45.119 --> 00:37:47.039
You have no idea
how long you were asleep.

00:37:47.639 --> 00:37:49.360
I waited for you for so long.

00:37:51.400 --> 00:37:55.199
The baby and I prayed
for you every single day.

00:37:57.559 --> 00:38:01.400
Now the three of us
are finally together again.

00:38:04.559 --> 00:38:06.159
You've been through so much.

00:38:19.840 --> 00:38:21.159
Watch your step, everyone.

00:38:21.159 --> 00:38:22.880
Take good care of yourselves out there.

00:38:23.800 --> 00:38:24.679
Don't push yourselves.

00:38:24.720 --> 00:38:26.270
If you can't keep going,
tell the team leader,

00:38:26.280 --> 00:38:27.290
and find a place to rest.

00:38:27.440 --> 00:38:28.159
Eat properly.

00:38:28.159 --> 00:38:29.039
Call every night.

00:38:29.119 --> 00:38:30.119
Don't worry.

00:38:31.440 --> 00:38:32.519
The world is so big.

00:38:32.719 --> 00:38:34.440
I should go see it too.

00:38:39.500 --> 00:38:40.320
I'm heading out then.

00:38:40.800 --> 00:38:41.719
I'll walk you down.

00:38:42.639 --> 00:38:43.119
Okay.

00:39:06.679 --> 00:39:07.199
Mom.

00:39:14.100 --> 00:39:15.390
I'll wait for you to come back.

00:39:18.159 --> 00:39:19.039
Don't worry.

00:39:19.800 --> 00:39:20.400
Go on back.

00:39:53.119 --> 00:39:53.719
Feng.

00:39:58.340 --> 00:39:59.239
Are you still leaving?

00:40:02.880 --> 00:40:03.480
No.

00:40:04.039 --> 00:40:05.580
Wherever you are, that's where I'll be.

00:40:26.519 --> 00:40:27.159
(You tell me,)

00:40:28.039 --> 00:40:29.320
(did they ever imagine)

00:40:29.480 --> 00:40:30.960
(that one day we would be reunited?)

00:40:31.800 --> 00:40:33.280
Do you think the two of them

00:40:34.740 --> 00:40:36.320
will ever have that day of recognition?

00:40:37.000 --> 00:40:38.800
(They probably didn't just imagine it.)

00:40:39.320 --> 00:40:42.159
(They must have believed it all along.)

00:40:44.199 --> 00:40:44.840
They will.

00:40:45.440 --> 00:40:46.840
That day will definitely come.

00:40:51.280 --> 00:40:52.880
Not only were we reunited,

00:40:53.519 --> 00:40:56.000
I think we didn't let them down.

00:40:57.510 --> 00:40:59.060
And we didn't let ourselves down either.

00:41:01.119 --> 00:41:02.679
When each of us is born,

00:41:03.559 --> 00:41:05.559
there are so many things
we cannot choose,

00:41:05.960 --> 00:41:07.800
like where we come from,
like blood ties.

00:41:08.559 --> 00:41:09.840
But we should thank ourselves

00:41:10.480 --> 00:41:12.039
for becoming who we wanted to be.

00:41:16.960 --> 00:41:19.159
(Qu Meng, Li Hongyue)
Mom, don't worry.

00:41:20.079 --> 00:41:21.719
The two of us will walk

00:41:22.519 --> 00:41:23.719
our path well.

00:41:25.440 --> 00:41:27.199
(Feng, Feifei)

00:41:27.639 --> 00:41:29.679
(I'm Mom, Qu Meng.)

00:41:31.760 --> 00:41:34.440
(In this lifetime, I've met many people)

00:41:35.039 --> 00:41:36.199
(and sung many songs.)

00:41:37.800 --> 00:41:40.760
(There are many people
in this world like your mother,)

00:41:41.360 --> 00:41:43.519
(who once lived on the edge of chaos,)

00:41:44.320 --> 00:41:48.039
(stumbling through right and wrong,
good and evil, all their lives.)

00:41:49.400 --> 00:41:51.440
(We are all ordinary beyond measure.)

00:41:52.559 --> 00:41:53.400
(We've been lost.)

00:41:54.079 --> 00:41:54.920
(We've been weak.)

00:41:56.039 --> 00:41:57.000
(We've been afraid.)

00:41:58.159 --> 00:42:00.719
(But the ones I love
taught me with their lives)

00:42:01.920 --> 00:42:02.679
(not to be afraid.)

00:42:03.719 --> 00:42:05.190
(Take one step forward with courage,)

00:42:05.719 --> 00:42:08.079
(Awake)
(the darkness will retreat one step.)

00:42:09.199 --> 00:42:10.960
(Light travels
through a thousand years,)

00:42:11.519 --> 00:42:13.559
(and every nightmare will awaken.)

00:42:15.079 --> 00:42:16.159
(Children, don't be afraid.)

00:42:17.280 --> 00:42:18.800
(I can already see you)

00:42:19.639 --> 00:42:21.920
(flying freely, riding the wind.)

00:42:23.559 --> 00:42:24.920
(The smiles on your faces)

00:42:25.239 --> 00:42:26.679
(are enough to light up the stars,)

00:42:27.760 --> 00:42:29.760
(blooming in the future.)

